{
  "chapter": 66,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十六回\"怒火\"。阿飞与林仙儿深夜对话，林仙儿试图挑拨阿飞与李寻欢的关系，以荆无命被上官金虹抛弃为例暗示李寻欢也会如此对待阿飞。阿飞坚定维护李寻欢，声明\"李寻欢是我的朋友，我不许任何人侮辱我的朋友\"，并指出荆无命的离开是主动选择而非被赶走。阿飞严厉要求林仙儿正视他，展露出前所未有的坚定意志。随后场景转向上官金虹，他正等待着什么人。阿飞假装入睡，实则清醒地感受到林仙儿在他身旁的诱惑。林仙儿趁阿飞\"熟睡\"后悄然离开，前往上官金虹处。上官金虹早已料到她会来，指出阿飞不如林仙儿想象中可靠。林仙儿以美色投靠上官金虹。阿飞目睹这一切，愤怒地闯入房间，林仙儿却冷漠地表示自己一向如此，嘲讽阿飞不该来。阿飞心如死灰，眼中泪光凝结成冰，绝望之色尽显。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "以前我也认为如此，但现在，我却已知道，有时活着还不如死了的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "这话简直不像你说的，就像李寻欢说的，只有像他这样孤独的人才会说得出这种可笑的话。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你认为这话很可笑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "当然可笑，假如每个人想法都和他一样，世上也不知有多少人早就该去死了，别人既然都不……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我不是别人，我就是我！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我发现你对他比对我好，是么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "可是，你为什么不想想，他总是要你为他杀人，我只不过是要你为我活下去，我对你难道不比他好得多？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "可是，我不能让他觉得我只要跟你在一起，就会消沉，我一定要他明白，我只有跟你在一起，才能振作！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我有时真不明白，你心里想的究竟是什么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我想的很简单，所以不会改变。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "永远也不会改变？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "永远！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我忽然发觉你和李寻欢之间的关系，很像上官金虹和荆无命。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "荆无命这个人几乎完全是为了上官金虹而活着的，上官金虹当然也对他很好，直到现在……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "现在荆无命已失去了利用的价值，立刻就被上官金虹像野狗般赶了出去，这样的结局，只怕是他做梦也想不到的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "也许他早就想到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "他若早知结局如此，还会那么样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "他会，因为他别无选择的余地。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "李寻欢对你好，只因为这世上惟有你才能真正地帮助他，除了你，他几乎完全孤立，但等你也没有利用价值的时候，他是不是也会像上官金虹对荆无命那样对你？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你回过头来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "回过头去？为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "因为我要告诉你两件事。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "这样我也能听得见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "但我却要你看着我，有些话，你不但要用耳朵听，还要用眼睛，否则你就永远不能了解它的意思。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你要对我说什么？我在听着。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我要你明白，李寻欢是我的朋友，我不许任何人侮辱我的朋友……任何人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "还有呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你刚才说的那些话，不但低估了我，也低估了荆无命。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "他？……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "他走，只因为他要走，并不是被人赶走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "可是，我不懂……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你不必懂，你只要记着。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你说的每一句话，我都永远记着，我只希望你也莫要忘记，你说过……你对我永远都不会变心的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "今天不要……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "今天你一定要好好休息，快睡吧，我会守在你旁边的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天晚上有人要来，我不许任何人打扰他。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "小飞你睡着了么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你早就算准我会来的，是不是？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "可是我……我自己却不知道我为什么要来。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你来，因为你已发现阿飞并不如你想像中那么可靠，你若还想活着，活得很好，就只有来投靠我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你……你可靠么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "那就得问你自己了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你一定会很可靠的，因为我永远不会让你觉得失望。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "抱起我，我……我已经走不动了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "到你这里来的人，难道都不敲门的吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "原来这人是疯子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "原来你竟是这种女人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你想不到么……其实我一直都是这种女人，从来也没有改变过，你想不到只因为你自己太愚蠢。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你只要稍微聪明些，就不该来的！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我已来了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你来了又有什么好处？难道还能咬我一口？……我跟你有什么关系？你能管得了我？我无论干什么，你都只有看着。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 331
    }
  ],
